# Anthropic Claude — set via `wrangler secret put ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` on the
# Worker. When this is unset, every text-generation path (chat, safety
# classifier, intake summary, engine routing, strengths summary, event
# cues) falls back to Cloudflare Workers AI (Llama) at lower quality.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6
AI_TEXT_MODEL=@cf/meta/llama-3.1-8b-instruct
AI_VISION_MODEL=@cf/llava-hf/llava-1.5-7b-hf
